title: Wednesday Post Show (03-09-22)
itunes:title: Wednesday Post Show (03-09-22)
description:
Bobby starts the show with a listener question for Eddie on being a new dad. Eddie reveals how he got through having his first kid. We get into a random discussion about the car Jaguars based on a news story. Eddie is hurt after a guy he was supposed to get lunch with ghosted him. We also get into a discussion of if we are optimistic or pessimistic.
